      <title>新西兰央行再次大幅降息，对冲基金转而看跌纽元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/hedge-funds-turn-bearish-on-kiwi-as-another-large-rbnz-cut-seen</link>
